ies%20like%20Langda%20or%20Gulab%20Khas%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20guarantees%20that%20the%20trees%20will%20flourish%20in%20their%20environment%20and%20bear%20fruit.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F416806%2Fhow-to-grow-kesar-mango-in-a-pot-steps-to-follow-location-temperature-gujarat-variety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKesar%20mango%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Maharashtra%20will%20not%20survive%20in%20Bengal%2C%20so%20we%20adapt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20carries%20out%20the%20germination%20and%20grafting%20process%20in%20two%20main%20locations%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Diamond%20Harbour%20and%20Burdwan%2C%20where%20the%20saplings%20are%20carefully%20nurtured%20before%20being%20distributed%20to%20farmers.%20One%20of%20his%20partners%2C%20Ashok%20Modi%2C%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20by%20generously%20providing%20land.%20He%20makes%20sure%20to%20help%20the%20entrepreneur%20in%20every%20way%20possible%2C%20to%20support%20his%20initiative.%20The%20grafting%20process%20is%20crucial%2C%20assuring%20that%20the%20mango%20trees%20are%20suited%20to%20the%20specific%20regional%20climate%2C%20which%20helps%20farmers%20grow%20healthy%20and%20fruitful%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-06T214301.806_11zon-1749226398.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrepreneur%20carries%20out%20the%20germination%20and%20grafting%20process%20in%20two%20main%20locations%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Diamond%20Harbour%20and%20Burdwan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-06T21430