ed%20strips%20of%20paracetamol%2C%20leftover%20antibiotics%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20flu%2C%20or%20a%20syrup%20bottle%20that%20was%20opened%20and%20forgotten.%20Most%20of%20us%20either%20flush%20these%20down%20the%20toilet%20or%20toss%20them%20in%20the%20bin.%20But%20did%20you%20know%20that%20these%20small%20actions%20can%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20our%20environment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hidden%20threat%20in%20your%20medicine%20cabinet%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20producers%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332843%2Fdr-pal-palaniappan-manickam-medical-comedy-show-weight-loss-intermittent-fasting-health-tips-standup-comedian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumers%20of%20pharmaceuticals%3C%2Fa%3E%20globally.%20According%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%20India%20generates%20approximately%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenterclimate.com%2Fbio-medical-waste-authorization%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAuthorisation%2520Requirements%2520of%2520Common%2520Biomedical%2Cas%2520per%2520the%2520SPCB%2FPCC.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20484%20tonnes%20of%20biomedical%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20day%2C%20a%20significant%20chunk%20of%20which%20includes%20unused%20and%20expired%20medicines%20from%20homes%2C%20clinics%20and%20pharmacies.%20Unfortunately%2C%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20nationwide%20system%20for%20collecting%20and%20safely%20disposing%20of%20household%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20medicines%20are%20flushed%20or%20dumped%20in%20landfills%2C%20their%20active%20ingredients%20can%20seep%20into%20soil%20and%20water%2C%20harming%20aquatic%20life%20and%20contaminating%20our%20drinking%20water.%20Studies%20have%20noted%20that%20improper%20disposal%20contributes%20to%20the%20growing%20problem%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1186%2Fs12982-025-00506-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAntibiotic%2520pollution%252C%2520originating%2520from%2520pharmaceutical%2Cand%2520advance%2520sustainable%2520pharmaceutical%2520manufacture.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20antimicrobial%20resistance%20(AMR%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20which%20makes%20common%20infections%20harder%20to%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengaluru%20alone%2C%20gaps%20in%20biomedical%20waste%20management%20have%20led%20to%20medicines%20being%20mixed%20with%20general%20waste%2C%20often%20ending%20up%20in%20open%20dumps%20or%20being%20burned%20in%20the%20open%2C%20releasing%20toxic%20fumes%20and%20posing%20risks%20to%20waste%20pickers%20and%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20can%20you%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20drug%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356074%2Fnikhil-lemos-meditel-innovation-multialarm-medication-reminder-unicef-david-beckham%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake-back%20programmes%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20disposal%20tricky%2C%20but%20there%20are%20safer%20ways%20to%20manage%20unused%20medicines%20responsibly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20flush%20them%20away%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlushing%20pills%20or%20pouring%20syrups%20down%20