%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDCFIGuoScTO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Nebula%20Space%20Organisation%20(%40nebulaspaceorg)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20monopoly%20in%20space%20manufacturing.%20We%20realised%20we%20could%20bypass%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Snehadeep.%20They%20cut%20the%20metal%20using%20CNC%20machines%2C%20ensuring%20precision%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20prototypes%20are%20modular%20and%20plug-and-play%2C%20almost%20like%20Lego%20sets.%20Controlled%20via%20a%20smartphone%20app%2C%20these%20CubeSats%20would%20provide%20real-time%20gamma%20radiation%20data%2C%20and%20even%20live%20camera%20feeds%20from%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManufacturing%20locally%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20saving%20money.%20It%20was%20a%20statement%3A%20space%20should%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20billion-dollar%20organisations.%20Their%20project%20showed%20that%20with%20innovation%20and%20resourcefulness%2C%20even%20college%20students%20could%20break%20into%20the%20space%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCreating%20our%20structures%20and%20PCBs%20allows%20us%20to%20be%20self-reliant%2C%20while%20also%20making%20it%20at%20a%20significantly%20lower%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Mohit%2C%20whose%20method%20will%20reduce%20the%20expense%20by%20125%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrash%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20problem%20in%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Snehadeep%20and%20Mohit%20are%20deeply%20conscious%20of%20another%20looming%20crisis%3A%20space%20debris.%20%E2%80%9CAryabhata%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20satellite%2C%20launched%20in%201975%2C%20is%20now%20space%20junk.%20No%20one%20even%20knows%20where%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Snehadeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nebula%E2%80%99s%20CubeSats%20can%20be%20designed%20with%20an%20end-of-life%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20solar%20sails%20%E2%80%94%20thin%2C%20reflective%20surfaces%20that%20harness%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20photon%20energy%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20deorbit%20after%20completing%20their%20mission.%20Instead%20of%20cluttering%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20orbit%2C%20the%20CubeSats%20would%20glide%20back%20into%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20disintegrate%20safely%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mohit%2C%20whose%20idea%20was%20to%20address%20space%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20is%20near%20the%20geo-signal%20orbit%2C%20then%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413019%2Fisro-yuvika-2025-class-9-students-apply-free-space-programme%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeasier%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20Earth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20have%20a%20GNSS%20system%20for%20tracking%20and%20a%20TLE%20address%2C%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20MAC%20address%20and%20IP%20address%20on%20our%20phones%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Snehadeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20solar%20sail%20will%20drag%20down%20the%20satellite%20to%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20atmosphere%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20somewhere%20in%20our%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20trajectory.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20find%20the%20geolocation%20of%20it%20and%20retrieve%20it.%20We%20will%20not%20be%20making%20any%20debris%20in%20space%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20add%20any%20more%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mohit%2C%20all%20of%20which%20can%20be%20monitored%20via%20an%20app%20that%20is%20being%20worked%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dual-purpose%20innovation%20%E2%80%94%20scientific%20exploration%20without%20environmental%20harm%20%E2%80%94%20is%20core%20to%20Nebula%20Space%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20ethos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20galaxy%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20intense%20theoretical%20and%20structural%20research%2C%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20prototype%20is%20ready%20on%20paper.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20see%20if%20our%20theoretical%20part%20works%2C%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20making%20this%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Snehadeep.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20practicality%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20then%20we%20need%20to%20start%20the%20theory%20from%20scratch%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COurs%20is%20verified%20and%20fact-checked%20by%20scientists%2C%20but%20making%20the%20final%20product%20is%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Snehadeep.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20put%20it%20into%20context%2C%20right%20now%2C%20people%20are%20venturing%20into%206G%20and%20researching%20it%2C%20but%20how%20to%20include%206G%20in%20individual%20phones%20is%20a%20huge%20challenge%2C%20which%20requires%20frequent%20testing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20four%20has%20submitted%20their%20research%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffirst-space-tourist-from-india-gopi-thotakura-shorts-spacetourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20international%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20their%20paper%20was%20accepted%20at%20the%20International%20Astronautical%20Congress%202024%20in%20Milan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20milestones%20for%20any%20emerging%20space%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22illustration%20of%20the%20satellite.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-20