ing%20solid%20waste%20and%20greywater%20has%20become%20essential%20to%20protect%20these%20mangroves.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20troubling%20is%20declining%20water%20quality%2C%20fuelled%20by%20greywater%20discharge%20and%20untreated%20runoff%20from%20nearby%20human%20settlements.%20Already%20operating%20in%20harsh%2C%20saline%2C%20and%20shifting%20tidal%20conditions%2C%20mangroves%20are%20now%20burdened%20by%20pollutants%20that%20push%20sensitive%20species%20to%20the%20brink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMangrove%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3EAvicennia%20marina%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20adapted%2C%20but%20others%20are%20disappearing%20from%20urban%20coastlines%20altogether%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%E2%80%99s%20the%20pressure%20of%20urban%20expansion.%20As%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20population%20grows%2C%20natural%20ecosystems%2C%20often%20dismissed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunused%E2%80%9D%2C%20become%20prime%20targets%20for%20development.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20areas%20need%20to%20be%20highlighted%20and%20protected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20urges.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20open%20land%3B%20they%20provide%20vital%20ecosystem%20services%20that%20cities%20depend%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMangroves%20may%20seem%20hardy%2C%20but%20beyond%20a%20point%2C%20degradation%20is%20irreversible%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20within%20a%20protected%20campus%2C%20the%20Godrej%20team%20finds%20itself%20constantly%20defending%20boundaries%20and%20biodiversity%2C%20holding%20the%20line%20against%20a%20tide%20of%20indifference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMangroves%20do%20what%20concrete%20can%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20the%20Wetlands%20Management%20Team%20continues%20to%20delve%20into%20conservation%2C%20and%20their%20efforts%20are%20paying%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mangroves%20act%20as%20a%20carbon%20sink%2C%20flood%20barrier%2C%20and%20bio-filtration%20system.%20It%E2%80%99s%20living%2C%20breathing%20climate%20infrastructure.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20underrated%20climate%20infrastructure%20we%20have.%20And%20yet%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20built%20over%20much%20of%20it%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20warns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20living%20example%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20possible%20when%20cities%20put%20nature%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Godrej%20has%20built%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20conservation%20story%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20replicable%20blueprint%20for%20urban%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rapidly%20expanding%20cities%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20pressure%20to%20convert%20every%20patch%20of%20green%20into%20grey%20is%20immense.%20Yet%20mangroves%20remind%20us%20that%20not%20all%20%E2%80%98vacant%E2%80%99%20land%20is%20unproductive%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20it%20is%20quietly%20doing%20the%20critical%20work%20that%20keeps%20cities%20liveable.%20From%20reducing%20the%20urban%20heat%20island%20effect%20and%20absorbing%20CO%E2%82%82%20to%20preventing%20floods%20and%20protecting%20coastal%20infrastructure%2C%20mangroves%20offer%20nature-based%20solutions%20to%20urban%20challenges%20that%20concrete%20can%E2%80%99t%20fix.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20could%20protect%20this%20in%20the%2080s%20%E2%80%94%20before%20ESG%2C%20before%20climate%20anxiety%20%E2%80%94%20then%20others%20can%20do%20it%20now.%20It%E2%80%99s%20never%20too%20late%20to%20let%20nature%20breathe%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20stop%20looking%20at%20natural%20ecosystems%20as%20land%20banks%20and%20start%20seeing%20them%20as%20living%20infrastructure%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejashree%20Joshi.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20a%20luxury%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20a%20necessity%20for%20future-ready%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22