summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20city%20where%20every%20inch%20of%20land%20is%20built%20upon%2C%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20chose%20to%20protect%20a%20forest%20instead.%20For%20over%20four%20decades%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20nurtured%20acres%20of%20mangroves%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20protecting%20biodiversity%2C%20preventing%20floods%2C%20and%20building%20a%20climate-resilient%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F444536%2Fmangrove-conservation-godrej-vikhroli-mumbai-species-biodiversity%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Jugaad%20Culture%20Through%20Stunning%20Photos%3A%20Inside%20the%20Lives%20of%20Those%20Who%20Fix%2C%20Reuse%20%26amp%3B%20Reinvent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20Sunday%20morning%20in%20May%20when%20I%20set%20out%20on%20a%20photo%20walk%20with%20my%20best%20friend%20through%20the%20old%20lanes%20of%20Lucknow.%20Having%20recently%20relocated%2C%20this%20was%20my%20first%20time%20back%20in%20the%20old%20city%20and%20just%20the%20thought%20of%20seeing%20its%20rustic%20monuments%2C%20crumbling%20bricks%2C%20and%20fading%20paint%20brought%20back%20memories%20of%20a%20slower%20time%20%E2%80%94%20a%20time%20when%20people%20valued%20what%20they%20had%20and%20chose%20to%20repair%2C%20not%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20six%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20the%20shops%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F431994%2Flucknow-bioscope-sanatkada-begum-akhtar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELucknow%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EChowk%20Bazaar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewere%20still%20shuttered%20as%20we%20set%20off%20on%20our%20little%20adventure%2C%20joined%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20like-minded%20folks%2C%20all%20curious%20and%20eager%20to%20freeze%20time%20through%20our%20lenses.%20As%20we%20walked%2C%20our%20organiser%20shared%20stories%20about%20the%20streets%2C%20including%20one%20about%20%3Cem%3EChor%20Bazaar%20(Thieves%E2%80%99%20Market)%20%3C%2Fem%3Enear%20Victoria%20Street.%20He%20told%20us%20it%20was%20once%20called%20%3Cem%3EShahi%20Bazaar%20(Royal%20Market)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20place%20where%20people%20still%20buy%20old%20clothes%2C%20second-hand%20watches%2C%20and%20even%20get%20their%20transistors%20repaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20moment%20reminded%20me%20of%20how%20deeply%20ingrained%3Cem%3E%20jugaad%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fem%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20making%20do%20with%20what%E2%80%99s%20available%20%E2%80%94%20is%20in%20our%20culture.%20My%20mind%20drifted%20to%20memories%20of%20my%20mother%20taking%20my%20worn-out%20shoes%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Emochi%20(cobbler)%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20stitching%2C%20or%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebartan%20wala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(utensil%20seller%20ot%20trader)%20who%20would%20roam%20our%20neighbourhood%2C%20trading%20old%20utensils%20for%20money.%20All%20signs%20of%20a%20quiet%20culture%20of%20repair%2C%20reuse%2C%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20World%20Environment%20Day%2C%20we%20celebrate%20that%20spirit%20%E2%80%94%20seen%20through%20the%20eyes%20and%20told%20in%20the%20words%20of%20talented%20photographers%20from%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJaipur%E2%80%99s%20handcrafted%20printing%20presses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FAD_4nXfQjaybc5FRw75rk-tRcdzX7KjANTbU9_q1hzSzINArUel8mJVHA0X8T3tbNed3nRKy0NUiiVCbtOyWsZ1srHpe