ry%20about%20innovation%20and%20alignment%20between%20farmer%20and%20factory%2C%20product%20and%20planet%2C%20and%20industry%20and%20intention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECan%20India%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biochemical%20hub%3F%20Absolutely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20something%20the%20world%20desperately%20needs%3A%20biomass%20and%20intent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20a%20biomass-rich%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avantika.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20have%20the%20raw%20material%20in%20abundance.%20We%20could%20even%20become%20the%20bioplastic%20and%20biochemical%20hub%20of%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStefan%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20chemical%20industry%20is%20coal-based.%20India%20has%20the%20biomass%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20leapfrog.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20reduce%20our%20environmental%20footprint%2C%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20survive.%20Nature%20will%20carry%20on%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we%20won%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pauses.%20%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%20that%20if%20the%20South%20Pole%20melts%20completely%2C%20the%20sea%20level%20could%20rise%20by%2060%20metres%3F%20That%20would%20wipe%20out%20most%20of%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20fertile%20land.%E2%80%9D%20It%E2%80%99s%20this%20urgency%20and%20opportunity%20that%20drives%20BCML%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20help%20make%20this%20bio-revolution%20happen%E2%80%A6%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20excites%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20future%20of%20plastics%20via%20Balrampur%20Bioyug%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Avantika%20envisions%20a%20future%20where%20BCML%20harnesses%20the%20full%20potential%20of%20PLA%20once%20the%20plant%20starts%20functioning%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20five%20years%2C%20I%20want%20to%20maximise%20the%20potential%20of%20PLA.%20